* Input is a numlist in the form "num1/num2" or "41/82"
capture program drop cnumlist
program cnumlist, rclass 
         version 13.1
         numlist `0'
         local result "`r(numlist)'"
         local result : subinstr local result " " ",", all
         return local numlist "`result'"
end
